&lt;조금 걸리는 게 있는데…&gt;
EN:
&lt;So something's been bothering me...&gt;

KR:
&lt;저 해적들… 확신에 차 있지 않았어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Wasn't it weird how they all seemed so... certain?&gt;

