&lt;…어쩔 생각이야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Well... What's the plan?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…오티스의 말대로 한 번 가보자.&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Let's try following Outis' plan.&gt;

KR:
&lt;천둥…?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Thunder...?&gt;

KR:
&lt;이렇게… 아무런 전조 없이 태풍 속에 들어왔다고…?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Wait... But the sky was clear just moments ago! How could this...?&gt;

